document_data.name: Muster at Eveningstar
document_data.mainbody: '''''Muster at Eveningstar''''' was a spell from the school of [[conjuration]].
document_data.Effects:
When cast, the spell teleported the caster to the Market Square in [[Eveningstar]].

This spell could only be cast once every half hour.
document_data.History: Ceremonial ''[[key to the city (Eveningstar)|keys to the city]]'' imbued with ''Muster at Eveningstar'' were distributed by Evenor [[Purple Dragons]] to those who aided the city.
